-- HTC CORP May Sales Fall 28.44% (Table) : 2498 TT
-- B y   J a n e t   O n g
-- 2012-06-06T09:04:55Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-06-06/htc-corp-may-sales-fall-28-44-table-2498-tt.html
HTC CORP (2498)  said unconsolidated sales
in May fell 28.44% to NT$29,057,335,000 from NT$40,603,199,000,
according to a statement filed to the  Taiwan Stock Exchange .  (Figures are in thousands of New Taiwan dollars)  =================================================================  5/2012           5/2011
Sales           29,057,335       40,603,199  
YOY%             -28.44%   -----------------Year-to-date-----------------
Sales          123,608,284      179,003,242  
YOY%             -30.95% 
=================================================================
 